>Description:
make-posn isn't bound for a Beginner executable
>How-To-Repeat:
Type the program
  (make-posn 1 2)
in DrScheme and save it to a file.

Set the language to Beginning Student

Create an executable

Run the executable => unbound variable `make-posn'

